//
// This plugin requires the RoundCube bridge to be enabled in Nextcloud.
// When using Roundcube embedded in Nextcloud via the nextcloud-roundcube app,
// enable "RoundCube bridge" in the Nextcloud admin settings.
//
// The plugin communicates with Nextcloud via the postMessage API to:
// - Attach files from Nextcloud to emails
// - Save email attachments to Nextcloud
// - Insert public share links into email body
// - Add calendar invitations (.ics) to Nextcloud Calendar
//
// No configuration is required here - the plugin automatically detects
// if the Nextcloud bridge is available.
